Package com.serezk4.command

Class Command

java.lang.Object
com.serezk4.command.Command
Direct Known Subclasses:
Add, Clear, ExecuteScript, Exit, Head, PrintFieldDescendingHairColor, RemoveById, RemoveFirst, RemoveGreater, Save, Show, SumOfHeight
public abstract class Command extends Object
Abstract base class representing a command.

A command encapsulates a specific operation that can be executed with a Request. Each command has a name, optional arguments, a help message, and a requirement for the number of elements needed to execute it.

Since:
1.0
